# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# Amma अम्मा — Environment Variables
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your keys.
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# ─── REQUIRED ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Google Gemini API Key (powers vision, voice, and classification)
# Get it: https://aistudio.google.com/apikey
GEMINI_API_KEY=

# ─── GREY ZONE WEB SEARCH ──────────────────────────────────────────────

# Serper.dev API Key (Google search for grey-zone classification)
# Get it: https://serper.dev (free $50 credit on signup)
SERPER_API_KEY=

# ─── WAKE WORD ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Picovoice Access Key (offline "Hey Amma" wake word detection)
# Get it: https://console.picovoice.ai (free tier available)
# Train custom keyword: https://console.picovoice.ai/ppn
PICOVOICE_ACCESS_KEY=

# ─── CLOUD BRAIN (Server) ─────────────────────────────────────────────

# Redis URL for session persistence
# Local dev: redis://localhost:6379
# Upstash (free serverless): https://console.upstash.com
# Fly.io: auto-set via `fly redis create`
REDIS_URL=

# Cloud Brain WebSocket URL (phone app connects here)
# Local dev: ws://localhost:8080
# Production: wss://amma-brain.fly.dev
CLOUD_BRAIN_URL=ws://localhost:8080

# ─── PERSISTENCE (Supabase) ───────────────────────────────────────────

# Gamification, Smriti memory, user data persistence
# Get it: https://supabase.com/dashboard (free tier: 500MB DB, 1GB storage)
SUPABASE_URL=
SUPABASE_KEY=

# ─── INTEGRATIONS (Optional) ──────────────────────────────────────────

# Google Calendar & Gmail OAuth
# Setup: https://console.cloud.google.com → APIs & Services → Credentials
# Enable: Google Calendar API, Gmail API
# Create: OAuth 2.0 Client ID (Desktop app)
# Download credentials.json to ~/.amma/
GOOGLE_CALENDAR_CREDENTIALS=~/.amma/credentials.json

# Spotify (music mood detection)
# Get it: https://developer.spotify.com/dashboard → Create App
SPOTIFY_CLIENT_ID=
SPOTIFY_CLIENT_SECRET=
SPOTIFY_REDIRECT_URI=http://localhost:8888/callback

# ─── PHONE APP ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# User ID for phone ↔ Cloud Brain pairing
AMMA_USER_ID=pranav

# ─── DEPLOYMENT (Fly.io) ──────────────────────────────────────────────

# Deploy token for CI/CD
# Install CLI: https://fly.io/docs/flyctl/install
# Get token: fly tokens create deploy
# Add as GitHub secret: FLY_API_TOKEN
FLY_API_TOKEN=
